snippet.title: Tales of Maj'Eyal 1.3.0 aka Dust to Dust Content Update Trailer
snippet.description:
http://www.gog.com/game/tales_of_majeyal

FREE Content Update for Tales of Maj'Eyal is now available along with a changleog that's too long for Youtube! 

Read all about it here: http://www.gog.com/forum/tales_of_majeyal/tales_of_majeyal_has_been_updated_to_version_130_aka_dust_to_dust 

or here: 

http://te4.org/blogs/darkgod/2015/03/news/tales-majeyal-130-aka-dust-dust-released
